Imagination changelog

0x/06/09 - 1.5:
		- Added audio support.
		- Added OGG slideshow export.
		- Added ability to randomly choose the transitions.
		- Grouped the transitions in family and added icons for describing the effect.
		- Added new transitions effects: Fade In and Fade Out to Fade family,
		  Barn Door Wipe family, Four Box Wipe and Ellipse Wipe.
		- Added man page.

26/02/09 - 1.0:
		- First release.
